content" class="main-content"> <a id="main-content" tabindex="-1"></a><div id="block-aw-page-title" class="page-title l-container"><h1>Die Seite wurde nicht gefunden</h1></div><div class="l-container content"><div id="block-hauptseiteninhalt"><div class="page-404"><div class="l-container l-container--small"><p class="t-align-center">Leider konnte unter der Webadresse keine Seite bei uns gefunden werden. Bei unserer Suche nach Transparenz in der Politik passiert uns das auch immer wieder. Erfreulich, wenn man Quellen für die weitere Suche findet:</p><div class="page-404__search"><form class="views-exposed-form" autocomplete="off" data-drupal-selector="views-exposed-form-aw-globale-suche-page-1" action="/suche" method="get" id="views-exposed-form-aw-globale-suche-page-1" accept-charset="UTF-8"><div class="textfield js-form-item form-item form-type-textfield js-form-type-textfield form-item-search-keys js-form-item-search-keys"> <label class="label" for="edit-search-keys">Suchbegriff(e)</label> <input data-lpignore="true" data-drupal-selector="edit-search-keys" type="text" id="edit-search-keys" name="search_keys" value="" size="30" maxlength="128" class="form-text textfield__input js-floating-label-trigger" /></div><div class="select js-form-item form-item form-type-select js-form-type-select form-item-search-api-datasource js-form-item-search-api-datasource"> <label class="label label--static" for="edit-search-api-datasource">Suche nach</label> <select data-drupal-selector="edit-search-api-datasource" id="edit-search-api-datasource" name="search_api_datasource" class="form-select js-select-replace"><option value="All" selected="selected">- Alle -</option><option value="entity:question_answer" >Frage/ Antwort</option><option value="entity:node" >Inhalt</option><option value="entity:politician" >Politiker:in</option> </select></div><div class="select js-form-item form-item form-type-select js-form-type-select form-item-type js-form-item-type"> <label class="label label--static" for="edit-type">Inhaltstyp</label> <select data-drupal-selector="edit-type" id="edit-type" name="type" class="form-select js-select-replace" data-drupal-states="{&quot;visible&quot;:{&quot;select[name=\u0022search_api_datasource\u0022]&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;entity:node&quot;}}}"><option value="All" selected="selected">- Alle -</option><option value="poll" >Abstimmung</option><option value="committee" >Ausschuss</option><option value="article_blog" >Blog-Artikel</option><option value="article_campaign" >Kampagne-Artikel</option><option value="newsletter" >Newsletter</option><option value="parliament_frontendpage" >Parlamentsseite</option><option value="petition" >Petition</option><option value="petition_update" >Petitionsupdate</option><option value="press_release" >Pressemitteilung</option><option value="article_research" >Recherche-Artikel</option><option value="landingpage" >Themenseite</option> </select></div><div data-drupal-selector="edit-actions" class="form-actions container js-form-wrapper form-wrapper" id="edit-actions"> <input data-drupal-selector="edit-submit-aw-globale-suche" type="submit" id="edit-submit-aw-globale-suche" value="Suchen" class="button js-form-submit form-submit button--icon-only" data-component-id="aw:button" /></div></form></div></div><div class="tile-wrapper"><div class="tile-wrapper__headline"><div class="l-container"><h2>Warum kann die Seite nicht angezeigt werden?</h2></div></div><div class="l-container"><div class="l-grid l-grid--medium-gutter"> <a class="reason-block l-grid__col l-grid__col--1/1 l-grid__col--1/2@sm l-grid__col--1/3@md" href=/profile><h3 class="reason-block__headline"> Fragen &amp; Antworten <span data-component-id="aw:icon" class="reason-block__icon icon-svg icon-svg--purple"> <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M9.41406 0.585938L22.8281 14L9.41406 27.4141L6.58594 24.5859L17.1719 14L6.58594 3.41406L9.41406 0.585938Z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span></h3><div class="reason-block__description"> Ähnlich wie manch ein Politiker können wir nicht alle Anfragen beantworten. Probieren Sie doch selber mal aus und befragen Sie Ihre Abgeordnete.</div></a><a class="reason-block l-grid__col l-grid__col--1/1 l-grid__col--1/2@sm l-grid__col--1/3@md" href=/recherchen/lobbyismus><h3 class="reason-block__headline"> Lobbyismus <span data-component-id="aw:icon" class="reason-block__icon icon-svg icon-svg--purple"> <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M9.41406 0.585938L22.8281 14L9.41406 27.4141L6.58594 24.5859L17.1719 14L6.58594 3.41406L9.41406 0.585938Z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span></h3><div class="reason-block__description"> Unangenehme Themen werden - nach Druck von außen - gerne mal unter den Teppich gekehrt.</div></a><a class="reason-block l-grid__col l-grid__col--1/1 l-grid__col--1/2@sm l-grid__col--1/3@md" href=/kampagnen/petitionen><h3 class="reason-block__headline"> Petition abgelehnt <span data-component-id="aw:icon" class="reason-block__icon icon-svg icon-svg--purple"> <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M9.41406 0.585938L22.8281 14L9.41406 27.4141L6.58594 24.5859L17.1719 14L6.58594 3.41406L9.41406 0.585938Z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span></h3><div class="reason-block__description"> Wir haben eine Petition eingereicht, um diese Seite doch noch anzeigen zu können. Unterstützen Sie uns!</div></a><a class="reason-block l-grid__col l-grid__col--1/1 l-grid__col--1/2@sm l-grid__col--1/3@md" href=/themen-dip21/umwelt><h3 class="reason-block__headline"> Klimawandel <span data-component-id="aw:icon" class="reason-block__icon icon-svg icon-svg--purple"> <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M9.41406 0.585938L22.8281 14L9.41406 27.4141L6.58594 24.5859L17.1719 14L6.58594 3.41406L9.41406 0.585938Z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span></h3><div class="reason-block__description"> Greta zwingt uns einen Teil der Server täglich für ein paar Stunden auszuschalten. Freitags sogar den ganzen Tag!</div></a><a class="reason-block l-grid__col l-grid__col--1/1 l-grid__col--1/2@sm l-grid__col--1/3@md" href=/recherchen/lobbyismus><h3 class="reason-block__headline"> Digitale Infrastruktur <span data-component-id="aw:icon" class="reason-block__icon icon-svg icon-svg--purple"> <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M9.41406 0.585938L22.8281 14L9.41406 27.4141L6.58594 24.5859L17.1719 14L6.58594 3.41406L9.41406 0.585938Z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span></h3><div class="reason-block__description"> Das Internet ist für uns in Deutschland #Neuland. Ja - immer noch!</div></a><a class="reason-block l-grid__col l-grid__col--1/1 l-grid__col--1/2@sm l-grid__col--1/3@md" href=/node/36><h3 class="reason-block__headline"> Entwicklung <span data-component-id="aw:icon" class="reason-block__icon icon-svg icon-svg--purple"> <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M9.41406 0.585938L22.8281 14L9.41406 27.4141L6.58594 24.5859L17.1719 14L6.58594 3.41406L9.41406 0.585938Z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span></h3><div class="reason-block__description"> Auch unsere Entwickler der Plattform machen mal einen Fehler - zum Glück können wir in unserem Fall schnell und unbürokratisch darauf reagieren.</div></a><a class="reason-block l-grid__col l-grid__col--1/1 l-grid__col--1/2@sm l-grid__col--1/3@md" href=/themen-dip21/lobbyismus-transparenz><h3 class="reason-block__headline"> Transparenz <span data-component-id="aw:icon" class="reason-block__icon icon-svg icon-svg--purple"> <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M9.41406 0.585938L22.8281 14L9.41406 27.4141L6.58594 24.5859L17.1719 14L6.58594 3.41406L9.41406 0.585938Z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span></h3><div class="reason-block__description"> Wir träumen von mehr Transparenz in der Politik. Manchmal aber scheinbar zu viel. Egal - träumen Sie mit uns.</div></a><a class="reason-block l-grid__col l-grid__col--1/1 l-grid__col--1/2@sm l-grid__col--1/3@md" href=/ueber-uns/spendenformular><h3 class="reason-block__headline"> Haushalt <span data-component-id="aw:icon" class="reason-block__icon icon-svg icon-svg--purple"> <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M9.41406 0.585938L22.8281 14L9.41406 27.4141L6.58594 24.5859L17.1719 14L6.58594 3.41406L9.41406 0.585938Z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span></h3><div class="reason-block__description"> Eine schwarze Zahl muss am Ende stehen, daher wurde die Seite aus Kostengründen gestrichen.</div></a><a class="reason-block l-grid__col l-grid__col--1/1 l-grid__col--1/2@sm l-grid__col--1/3@md" href=/kampagnen/petitionen><h3 class="reason-block__headline"> Flüchtlingspolitik <span data-component-id="aw:icon" class="reason-block__icon icon-svg icon-svg--purple"> <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M9.41406 0.585938L22.8281 14L9.41406 27.4141L6.58594 24.5859L17.1719 14L6.58594 3.41406L9.41406 0.585938Z" fill="currentColor" /></svg></span></h3><div class="reason-block__description"> Glauben Sie doch selber nicht, oder?</div></a></div></div><div class="tile-wrapper__headline"><div class="l-container"><h2>Vielleicht interessiert Sie einer unserer aktuellen Artikel aus unseren Recherchen, unseren Kampagnen oder unserem Blog:</h2></div></div></div><div class="views-element-container container"><div class="js-view-dom-id-554cf66d2fe39c8929619c379f46cacb5000fc75d0e3d276ea4021cfd688c754 view-aw-404-page-last-articles"><div class="l-container"><div class="l-grid l-grid--medium-gutter"> <article class="tile l-grid__col l-grid__col--min-width l-grid__col--1/2@xs 